Maurice Black https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maurice_Black 0 Maurice Black (January 14, 1891 – January 18, 1938) was an American character actor known for his portrayal of mobsters. He appeared in more than 100 films from 1928 to 1938, when he died of pneumonia, aged 47. He was married to Edythe Raynore.
